==Russian==

===Verb===
'''ездить''' (jézdit’) ''(abstract verb, [[impf.]])'', [[ехать]] (jéχat’) ''(concrete verb, [[impf.]])'', [[поехать]] (pojéχat’) ''(concrete verb, [[pf.]])''

# to be [[going]], to [[go]], to be in the habit of [[going]] ''(in a conveyance or on horseback)''
# to [[ride]], to [[drive]]
# to [[travel]]
#:*{{RUchar|Я [[часто|ча́сто]] е́зжу в [[Москва|Москву́]]}} ''(abstract)'' — ''I frequently go (travel) to Moscow.''
#:*{{RUchar|Я е́ду в [[Москва|Москву́]]}} ''(concrete)'' — ''I’m going to Moscow (right now).''

